description: Try our easy to follow Roast Green Beans With Sweet Tomatoes recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Roast vegetable,Low saturated fat,Roast,Low salt,Christmas,Wheat free,Tomato,Low sugar
name: Roast Green Beans With Sweet Tomatoes Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 220Â°C. Trim 400g beanettes and blanch in boiling, salted water for 1 minute then drain. Scatter beans on a baking tray. Add 2 punnets Sweet Solanto tomatoes, 2 sliced garlic cloves, 1/2 cup pitted Kalamata olives and 6 peeled, halved eschallots. Drizzle with 2 tbs olive oil. Scatter with 200g crumbled feta. Roast for 15 minutes. Remove from oven, drizzle with 1 tbs balsamic vinegar, season with salt and pepper and toss gently. Transfer to a serving dish and finish with 2 tbs basil leaves.
